      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute stunner. It\u2019s in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
