    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system in peak operational health. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with precise linkage and a robust clutch engagement. The chassis maintains factory-spec kinematics with a functional M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring exceptional power delivery through the rear wheels. Finished in a flawless coat with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of oxidation or fluid seepage, making it a definitive example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
