      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously preserved in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or door dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease, and the original factory floor mats look untouched. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, documented service history and having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. It drives with the same precision and tightness as the day it was first delivered. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a pristine, collector-grade example.",
